    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Nice beginning there :) \nI think this map can be very interesting (the Heavy Bomb. version is much better in terms of eco btw !).\n\nHowever, the original map is still highly unbalanced, in favor of southern island. \nSeveral major issues on this map : \n- the central mountain on North island prevents from building there. It should be totally removed\n- also, southern shores seem to be more accessible (compare the (new) C and D spots)\n- oil derricks : southern oil derricks are on 1 spot, so more easily defendable by a group of infantry\n- finally, maybe expanding the limits of the map (is this possible with current Map Editor ?), so that naval maneuvers become easier, instead of having to deal with narrow water corridors ... \n"
  },
