    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "The main issue about these map alterations is the balance between making the map more player balanced and retaining the maps' original properties. Until we have maps that outright replaces the current maps in the map pool I'm hesitent to alter the originals much beyond what the original creator made them to be. Sooner or later a map will come a long to push this map off its place but until that happens I'd like to have this map present certain standards of which map makers can size themselves against, but I'm not willing to put in the effort to recreate them much beyond design.\n\nThus I agree with all your points but I'd much rather see work put down on creating something new rather than remodeling originals much beyond their original design.\n"
  },
